title: W.A. Mozart - Idomeneo - Gardiner 1991 [FLAC]
description:
Idomeneo, re di Creta ossia Ilia e Idamante
(Italian: Idomeneo, King of Crete, or, Ilia and Idamante; usually referred to simply as Idomeneo, K. 366) is an Italian opera by Wolfgang Amadeus Mozart. The libretto was adapted by Giambattista Varesco from a French text by Antoine Danchet.

# Audio CD (September 12, 1991)
# SPARS Code: DDD
# Number of Discs: 3
# Label: Archiv Produktion

Artists: John Eliot Gardiner (conductor), English Baroque Soloists, Anthony Rolfe Johnson, Anne Sofie von Otter, Hillevi Martinpelto, Sylvia McNair, Nigel Robson, Glenn Winslade
